      public Screening addScreening(Movie movie, Cinema cinema, int year, int month, int day, int hour, int minute) throws Exception
      Add new screening
      Parameters:
      movie - movie object
      cinema - cinema the screening will take place in
      year - year of screening
      month - month of screening
      day - day of screening
      hour - hour of screening
      minute - minute of screening
      Returns:
      screening object that has been successfully added
      Throws:
      Exception - if screening already exists or movie's showing status is end of showing
